The paper proposes a sequence-to-sequence neural network model for generating titles for web tables. This involves extracting text snippets and using both copy and generation mechanisms in the decoder to balance relevance and readability of the generated title. This approach falls under the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI), and deep learning (cs.DL).
